      <li style="padding: 0.25rem 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 0.875rem;">&#10003; Gmail</li>
      <li style="padding: 0.25rem 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 0.875rem;">&#10003; Google Calendar</li>
      <li style="padding: 0.25rem 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 0.875rem;">&#10003; Google Drive</li>
      <li style="padding: 0.25rem 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 0.875rem;">&#10003; Granola <em>(recommended — works with Zoom, Teams, Google Meet)</em></li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;"><strong>Where to check:</strong> Settings &rarr; Connected Apps (claude.ai) or Settings &rarr; Connectors (Cowork/Desktop)</p>
  </CalloutBox>

